s video series on Sage Patanjali’s Yogasutras . \n\nThese audio recordings are crisp, short and to the point. Remember, it is easy to complicate any topic but equally difficult to simplify it. I decided to simplify it without compromising on its essence. Most important thing about these series is that it tries to bring forth the practical application of all the 195 Yogasutras. \n\nThis text helped me make my life beautiful and so I had to upload it at the earliest because I knew it will help solve many of my listeners problems too and make their life beautiful. \n\nSo, listen to it with an open heart, contemplate over one sutra everyday, apply it wherever and whenever possible and see the magic of the Yogasutras unfold. \n\nHappy learning my dear friends. Have a great life.\n\n———————————————————————————\n\nTo support my channel:\n\nLike, subscribe and hit the bell icon.\n\nTell fellow learners to do the same.\n\nDonate via PayPal : https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=EHHLRNCPRJM4W&source=url\n\nEnrol for Patanjali’s Yogasutras Crash Course in 4 Hrs - https://www.udemy.com/patanjalis-yogasutras-in-4-hrs/\n\nEnrol for ChantSutra, Patanjali Yogasutra chanting with word breakup - https://www.udemy.com/chantsutra-patanjali-yogasutra-with-meaning\n\nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/pravzyoga \n\nInstagram : https://Instagram.com/pravzyoga \n\nYouTube Channel - https://www.youtube.com/user/impravz\n\n#patanjali #yogasutra #patanjalis #yogasutras #yoga #philosophy #indianphilosophy #yogaphilosophy #pravz #DrPraveenaShetty #sutra #sutras #samkhya #sankhya #shaddarshan #hindi #scripture #scriptures #qci #ryt", "channel_id": "UCv_8zqzprhGtl_pzawJ0muw", "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCv_8zqzprhGtl_pzawJ0muw", "duration": 60, "view_count": 436, "age_limit": 0, "webpage_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7D5yi_NusTA", "categories": ["People & Blogs"], "tags": [], "playable_in_embed": true, "live_status": "not_live", "media